title: Watch: This is what it looks like to hit jelly with a tennis racket in slow motion
text:
This is really, bizarrely satisfying.
Why would The Slow Mo Guys whack some jelly with some tennis rackets? The real question is 'why not?'.
Although we have to admit, this is one of the ones we're glad we get to watch and not partake in. That would be far too sticky for our liking.
Via YouTube
